# Content Helpers

```scala
val name = "World"
val greeting = md"""
  Hello, $name!
  Welcome to ScalaScript.
"""
println(greeting)
```

```scala
def section(title: String, items: List[String]) =
  doc(s"[$title]", items.mkString("\n"))

render(section("Items", List("one", "two", "three")))
```
